      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IMPRESS CARMEN (2) hit the frame two back then broke through last time by one length (22.89) at Mandurah over 400m. Drawn well off an inside draw. Maiden this journey but has some solid runs behind her. The one to beat again. CANDY MONELLI (1) boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 1.3 lengths (17.44) behind Freckles Monelli at Mandurah. Can feature again. ELITE ARNOTT (7) was popular in betting last start but disappointed when 5.5 lengths away in fourth (22.42). Finished third the start before. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. One of the better chances. ORANA JET (5) must be included on latest effort.",
